message.content:
Monday:
- Breakfast: Avocado toast with cherry tomatoes and a side of freshly squeezed orange juice.
- Lunch: Quinoa salad with roasted vegetables, lemon-tahini dressing, and grilled chicken.
- Dinner: Grilled salmon with steamed broccoli and brown rice.

Tuesday:
- Breakfast: Green smoothie with spinach, banana, almond milk, and flaxseeds.
- Lunch: Vegetable stir fry with tofu and brown rice noodles.
- Dinner: Lentil soup with a side of whole grain bread.

Wednesday:
- Breakfast: Chia seed pudding with fresh berries and almond milk.
- Lunch: Grilled chicken salad with mixed greens, cucumber, cherry tomatoes, and balsamic vinaigrette.
- Dinner: Vegetable curry with basmati rice.

Thursday:
- Breakfast: Oatmeal with sliced fruit and walnuts.
- Lunch: Grilled shrimp salad with mixed greens, cherry tomatoes, cucumber, and lemon vinaigrette.
- Dinner: Baked salmon with roasted vegetables and quinoa.

Friday:
- Breakfast: Vegetable omelette with spinach, bell peppers, and onions.
- Lunch: Grilled chicken wrap with mixed greens, cherry tomatoes, cucumber, and hummus.
- Dinner: Vegetable stir fry with tofu and brown rice noodles.

Saturday:
- Breakfast: Green smoothie with banana, almond milk, spinach, and flaxseeds.
- Lunch: Grilled chicken salad with mixed greens, cherry tomatoes, cucumber, and balsamic vinaigrette.
- Dinner: Vegetable curry with basmati rice.

Sunday:
- Breakfast: Avocado toast with cherry tomatoes and a side of freshly squeezed orange juice.
- Lunch: Grilled shrimp salad with mixed greens, cherry tomatoes, cucumber, and lemon vinaigrette.
- Dinner: Baked salmon with roasted vegetables and quinoa.
